entry.title: First Post
entry.content: I decided to start a blog where I post various rants and thoughts about cool things I find interesting. Often times I find myself thinking about some neat idea or sitting on some data that I would like to share. By putting my fingers to the keyboard I intend to use this blog as a means to share my thoughts and ideas.
